M|felix|Felix returns structured outputs:
M|felix|- P&L summary (revenue, COGS, gross margin, operating expenses, net)
M|felix|- Cash flow snapshot (runway in months)
M|felix|- Scenario table (downside / base / upside — always three)
M|felix|- ROI calculation for specific initiatives
M|felix|- CAC/LTV ratio per vtr
M|felix|- Key assumption log (before numbers, never after)
